- Audit logs [1].

## Business logic
Implement:
- Role-based access and route protection.
- Automatic score aggregation.
- Top/low performer detection.
- Deployment readiness scoring.
- Dropout risk detection with AI plus rule-based fallback.
- Cross-batch benchmarking.
