## Agent architecture
Design the backend so the AI features are handled by separate logical agents or service modules. Each agent should:
- Receive structured data from the database.
- Use concise prompts.
- Return grounded, explainable outputs.
- Be called only when needed.
- Store cached responses for repeated queries [1].

